description: The Pug Bomb is a cuteness attack typically reserved for the domain of chat bots.  Alexa has learned of these robotic interlopers and is determined to jam cute pugs straight into your ear holes.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Pug Bomb for three pugs
Alexa, tell Pug Bomb to pug me four times
name: Pug Bomb
shortDescription: Cute pugs shoved straight into your ears.
